name: aliexpress.solution.feed.invalidate
description: Api for invalidating specific feeds based on job Ids. Please use aliexpress.solution.feed.list.get to determine which job Ids needs to be sent for invalidation.

requestParams.name: job_id_list
requestParams.description: job id separated by ;  No more than 100 job Ids could be passed in one request.

responseParams.name: no_need_invalidation_list
responseParams.description: no need to be invalidated jobs. Usually caused by that the job is being or has already been executed.
